OL,3,C'The first 100k views felt amazing':
OL,4,CSocial media pets paying the bills
OL,6,FThe most popular social media posts
OL,7,Fcan gain millions of views, as ITV
OL,8,FNews' Consumer Editor Chris Choi
OL,9,Freports.
OL,11,FBruno the cross-breed Dalmatian is a
OL,12,Ftrue wags-to-riches story.
OL,14,FA stray from Spain, he was eventually
OL,15,Frehomed in the UK - but his new owners
OL,16,Fhad problems getting him to respond to
OL,17,Fcommands.
OL,19,FIn desperation, they even learned
OL,20,FSpanish to talk to him - but that
OL,21,Fdidn't help.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776819790
OL,3,C'The first 100k views felt amazing':
OL,4,CSocial media pets paying the bills
OL,6,FWhen he didn't react to a pan falling
OL,7,Fbehind him, they realised Bruno was
OL,8,Fdeaf.
OL,10,FThey started using sign language and
OL,11,Fposted a video about it.
OL,13,FHis owner, Skye Tibbetts, told ITV's
OL,14,FTonight programme: "I just uploaded
OL,15,Fit, his very first video, then we went
OL,16,Ffor a walk."
OL,18,FBy the time they returned, it had
OL,19,Fthousands of views.
OL,26,@vD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
