OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776819790
OL,3,C'The first 100k views felt amazing':
OL,4,CSocial media pets paying the bills
OL,6,F"We didn't realise it would be a big
OL,7,Fdeal... I went, 'darling, I think this
OL,8,Fmight be going viral'."
OL,10,FSince then, he's got 14,000 TikTok
OL,11,Ffollowers and a #1,000 deal to promote
OL,12,Fdog food.
OL,14,FSkye says this is a sideline where
OL,15,Fcare must always come before cash.
OL,17,F"Bruno, even before we started doing
OL,18,Fcontent, he was the centre of our
OL,19,Fworld," she told us.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
