OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776819790
OL,3,C'The first 100k views felt amazing':
OL,4,CSocial media pets paying the bills
OL,6,F"He was the ring-bearer at our
OL,7,Fwedding, and our life was sort of
OL,8,Fbuilt around him. So content creation
OL,9,Fis just capturing that."
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FWe have been inside the lucrative
OL,17,Fworld of the UK's social media pet
OL,18,Fstars.
