OL,3,C'The first 100k views felt amazing':
OL,4,CSocial media pets paying the bills
OL,6,FSome are viewed hundreds of millions
OL,7,Fof times, earning enough to help pay
OL,8,Fowners' bills.
OL,10,FRecent research of thousands of animal
OL,11,Fowners suggests more than a quarter
OL,12,Fhave set up an account for their pets.
OL,13,FIt's a global trend, with the biggest
OL,14,Fpet stars now attracting payments up
OL,15,Fto #30,000 a post.
OL,17,FOur furry friends are a surging
OL,18,Fdigital market anticipated to be worth
OL,19,Falmost #3 billion globally by 2033.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
