OL,3,C'The first 100k views felt amazing':
OL,4,CSocial media pets paying the bills
OL,6,FFeline fame is a big part of the
OL,7,Ftrend, with cats reportedly generating
OL,8,Fup to #12,000 per video.
OL,10,FAlthough not at that level yet, Mia, a
OL,11,Ffluffy white cat from Bolton, is well
OL,12,Fon her way.
OL,14,FShe has had hundreds of millions of
OL,15,Fviews on social media.
OL,17,F"When we started filming, it wasn't
OL,18,Fprofessional in any way ...when she
OL,19,Fgot the first hundred thousand views,
OL,20,Fit obviously felt amazing," her owner,
OL,21,FDmytro Vnukov, explained.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
