OL,3,C'The first 100k views felt amazing':
OL,4,CSocial media pets paying the bills
OL,6,FMarketing experts found that consumers
OL,7,Ffind pets more persuasive than people.
OL,8,FAnimals aren't insincere and therefore
OL,9,Fare seen as more trustworthy in
OL,10,Fadverts. But pet owners need to stick
OL,11,Fto the rules.
OL,13,FAnyone who receives a benefit from a
OL,14,Fbrand by posting on social media needs
OL,15,Fto label their content as advertising.
OL,16,FAlso, if you earn more than #1,000
OL,17,Ffrom your pet, you will need an animal
OL,18,Fperformance licence from your local
OL,19,Fcouncil.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
