OL,3,C'The first 100k views felt amazing':
OL,4,CSocial media pets paying the bills
OL,6,FLayla Flaherty is an agent who
OL,7,Frepresents hundreds of pet stars - her
OL,8,Fown dachshund advertised for a major
OL,9,Fsupermarket.
OL,11,F"We have lizards, we have snakes, we
OL,12,Fhave alpacas - we've got everything...
OL,13,FAs long as you are willing to dedicate
OL,14,Fthe time, there is money to be made,"
OL,15,Fshe told ITV Tonight.
OL,17,FMany of the animals in her books
OL,18,Fstarted on social media before going
OL,19,Fon to adverts and even Hollywood.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
