OL,3,C'The first 100k views felt amazing':
OL,4,CSocial media pets paying the bills
OL,6,FFor the highest earners, she says,
OL,7,F"you're talking probably a minimum of
OL,8,Fa thousand pounds a day".
OL,10,FBut, she cautions: "We will only ever
OL,11,Fwork with pet parents that have their
OL,12,Fpet's interests at heart."
OL,14,FThe RSPCA doesn't object in principle,
OL,15,Fbut stresses that animals should only
OL,16,Fbe filmed if they are comfortable,
OL,17,Fsafe and exhibiting their natural
OL,18,Fbehaviour.
