OL,3,C'The first 100k views felt amazing':
OL,4,CSocial media pets paying the bills
OL,6,FAnti-cruelty investigators are
OL,7,Fconcerned about some worrying social
OL,8,Fmedia trends.
OL,10,FThe RSPCA's Intelligence Manager, Sam
OL,11,FBradley, showed Tonight videos of cats
OL,12,Fbeing dropped onto tinfoil.
OL,14,F"The cats predominantly react by
OL,15,Fjumping away immediately, almost as if
OL,16,Fthey've received an electric shock,"
OL,17,Fhe said.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
