OL,3,C'The first 100k views felt amazing':
OL,4,CSocial media pets paying the bills
OL,6,F"And the reaction of people in the
OL,7,Fvideos makes it obvious that it's
OL,8,Fsomething they find really amusing -
OL,9,Fbut it's quite clear the animals are
OL,10,Fin distress."
OL,12,FA young pet owner in Manchester is
OL,13,Fshowing that, for those who put their
OL,14,Fpet's interest first, social media can
OL,15,Fbe life-changing.
OL,17,FLeon, 17, has reached 700,000
OL,18,FInstagram followers in just a year,
OL,19,Fposting videos of his dog walks with
OL,20,FShadow, a large and muscular mastiff.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
