OL,3,C'The first 100k views felt amazing':
OL,4,CSocial media pets paying the bills
OL,6,F"For me to be able to create a social
OL,7,Fmedia account and start a job with
OL,8,FShadow, start a company, it's
OL,9,Fabsolutely amazing," he told us.
OL,11,F"The way that we started off, we were
OL,12,Fnot looking to get paid, it wasn't for
OL,13,Frevenue. It was just to share the
OL,14,Fawareness that big dogs are friendly."
OL,16,FAs families' financial reserves run
OL,17,Flow, some are getting a budget boost
OL,18,Ffrom pet power.
